prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D cartoon illustration for a greeting card front. The style is dreamy fantasy with a humorous twist.

The scene is set on a magical, pastel-colored beach under a twilight sky with shimmering stars and two moons. In the center, characters based on Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are having a surreal birthday celebration.

Jordan, the dog, is depicted as a cartoon dog-human hybrid, comically lounging in a giant, ornate seashell throne like a king. He's wearing a tiny, crooked birthday party hat and a magnificent royal cape. He has an exaggeratedly happy, slightly clueless expression as he gestures with one paw towards Lao Lao.

Lao Lao, the person from the photo, is illustrated in her blue sweatshirt, looking amused and slightly exasperated. She is comically serving Jordan, holding a silver platter that, instead of a cake, has a single, perfect dog biscuit with a glowing birthday candle on it. Colorful, floating dog toys (a squeaky ball, a rope toy) drift around them like planets. The waves gently washing ashore are made of iridescent bubbles.

In the center of the image, floating in the sky above the characters in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao".
